            "html": "<p class=\"q-text qu-display--block qu-wordBreak--break-word qu-textAlign--start\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">Try thinking of </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; background: none;\">investing in bitcoin</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\"> as you would buying a lottery ticket. It only costs a dollar, but you could win big. However, as historically shown with commodities, the odds are good that you're going to lose money compared with a low-cost, diversified </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; background: none;\">investment</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">.Bitcoin is open to everyone and provides an exciting opportunity to delve into an entirely new asset class.</span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block qu-wordBreak--break-word qu-textAlign--start\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">Investing in bitcoin may seem scary, but know that it takes time and effort to understand how Bitcoin works.</span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block qu-wordBreak--break-word qu-textAlign--start\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">Also keep in mind that the Bitcoin are varied. Keep that in mind, and do your own research based on where you live.</span></p>",
